{"id": "software-development--meshcore-cuda-keygen", "title": "Meshcore-CUDA-Keygen", "forum": "software-development", "messages": [{"id": "1451448742866714654", "author": "Devin Frederick", "author_handle": "dfred18", "user_id": "468963080475377669", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/468963080475377669/e88953b60c0c9ba297abd2030b1df4d3.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, December 19, 2025 12:39 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-19 12:39 a.m.", "text": "This program is based on the web keygen by \" https://github.com/agessaman/meshcore-web-keygen \" but has been ported to run on modern Nvidia graphics cards. This just speeds up the custom prefix finding. I am getting a little over 4M keys per second tried as compared to the 7k in the web version. I will be putting the source code on github soon.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>This program is based on the web keygen by &quot;<a href=\"https://github.com/agessaman/meshcore-web-keygen\">https://github.com/agessaman/meshcore-web-keygen</a>&quot; but has been ported to run on modern Nvidia graphics cards. This just speeds up the custom prefix finding. \n\n I am getting a little over 4M keys per second tried as compared to the 7k in the web version. \n\nI will be putting the source code on github soon.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451448742866714654/1451448743051395072/Screenshot_2025-12-19_002434.png?ex=69ec537a&amp;is=69eb01fa&amp;hm=2b30814c966b45ef831be9ba05e580c74a7f32a1c2f0c388c0046da78039613b&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451448742866714654/1451448743051395072/Screenshot_2025-12-19_002434.png?ex=69ec537a&amp;is=69eb01fa&amp;hm=2b30814c966b45ef831be9ba05e580c74a7f32a1c2f0c388c0046da78039613b&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: Screenshot_2025-12-19_002434.png (110.55 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=muscle><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=💪 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f4aa.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>2</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1451461753564041342", "author": "Uncle Lit", "author_handle": "unclelit", "user_id": "84097297872322560", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, December 19, 2025 1:30 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-19 1:30 a.m.", "text": "look forward to testing it with a 5090!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>look forward to testing it with a 5090!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1452813969944346705", "author": "Uncle Lit", "author_handle": "unclelit", "user_id": "84097297872322560", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, December 22, 2025 7:04 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-22 7:04 p.m.", "text": "@Devin Frederick is it ready for public test?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"dfred18\">@Devin Frederick</span> is it ready for public test?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1452814231253811315", "author": "Devin Frederick", "author_handle": "dfred18", "user_id": "468963080475377669", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/468963080475377669/e88953b60c0c9ba297abd2030b1df4d3.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday